Snap:H
  H:MusuCursor,Run
    A:MusuCursor
      self,round=4	{"mung":["age"]}
      w:MusuCursor
        self,round=4	{"mung":["age"]}
        req:wrangle,eternal,ok
        testing
          reached:step_2
          Dogear,of:record-t1
            curs,Mag:Musica
              curs,wild:Cloud,randomic:draw_one
                curs,wild:Record,id:t1
          Dogear,of:cloud-two
            curs,Mag:Musica
              curs,wild:Cloud,randomic:draw_two
          resolved:hit,depth=3,ok,id:t1
          resolved:cloud,depth=2,ok,randomic:draw_two,cloud_type
          see:a cursor is a stack of matches — resolving one re-finds every level from the magazine down and lands on the exact record it names
          see:a cursor can name a level not just a leaf — a two-deep cursor lands on the cloud and stops there
          reached:step_4
          resolved:gone,depth=2,failed,missing_id:t1
          see:when a named level is gone the cursor fails cleanly — it reports the exact match it could not find and how far it got not a crash
        Mag:Musica
          Cloud,randomic:draw_one,created_at=1000
            Record,id:t2,artist:Bassbin,title:Two,path:crate/b/two.opus
          Cloud,randomic:draw_two,created_at=2000
            Record,id:t3,artist:Cutter,title:Three,path:crate/c/three.opus
